OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,FThe NHS is urging patients not to put
OL,7,Foff seeking the care they need as
OL,8,Fresident doctors press ahead with
OL,9,F"difficult" strike action, which the
OL,10,FHealth Secretary has branded
OL,11,F"disappointing".
OL,13,FTens of thousands of resident doctors
OL,14,Fin England are to stage a six-day
OL,15,Fwalkout on Tuesday, immediately after
OL,16,Fthe Easter weekend.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@KO]sD@AOUsD@OO]
