PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,FNHS England said hospital teams across
OL,7,Fthe country will be working to
OL,8,Fminimise disruption for patients
OL,9,Fduring the walkout, which is "expected
OL,10,Fto be particularly challenging"
OL,11,Fbecause of a shorter notice period.
OL,13,FThe strikes are going ahead after the
OL,14,FGovernment took a key part of its
OL,15,Foffer off the table.
OL,17,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,18,FCare said last week that an offer of
OL,19,F1,000 extra training places would no
OL,20,Flonger be "financially or
OL,21,Foperationally" possible.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@_O]|D@KOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
