OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,FDuring the six-day action, patients
OL,7,Fare urged to attend planned
OL,8,Fappointments unless they have been
OL,9,Fcontacted to reschedule, and those
OL,10,Fwith life-threatening emergencies
OL,11,Fshould still call 999 or attend A&E.
OL,13,FProfessor Ramani Moonesinghe, national
OL,14,Fclinical director for critical and
OL,15,Fperioperative care at NHS England,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Staff across the NHS will be
OL,17,Fdoing everything they can this week to
OL,18,Fkeep patients safe and ensure people
OL,19,Fcan continue to get the care they
OL,20,Fneed," said Prof Moonesinghe.
OL,26,@xD@GOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
