OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,F"We know this round of industrial
OL,7,Faction will be difficult, coming
OL,8,Fstraight after the Easter weekend, but
OL,9,Fpatients should come forward as normal
OL,10,Fand attend any appointments unless
OL,11,Fthey are contacted otherwise.
OL,13,F"The NHS remains open for you this
OL,14,Fweek ` as ever, please call 999 or
OL,15,Fcome to A&E in an emergency, and use
OL,16,F111 online first if you need urgent
OL,17,Fbut not life-threatening help."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
