PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,7,F"It is disappointing for patients and
OL,8,Fstaff alike that the BMA has decided
OL,9,Fto press ahead with strikes this week,
OL,10,Fdespite the deal we put to them which
OL,11,Fwould have seen resident doctors 35.2%
OL,12,Fbetter off, on average, than they were
OL,13,Ffour years ago.
OL,15,F"My attention and that of leaders
OL,16,Facross the NHS is now on protecting
OL,17,Fpatients and staff by minimising
OL,18,Fdisruption to the health service.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,F"Thanks to the dedication of talented
OL,7,FNHS staff, the health service
OL,8,Fdelivered almost 95% of planned
OL,9,Factivity during December strikes, and
OL,10,FI want to reassure patients that the
OL,11,FNHS will be there for you when you
OL,12,Fneed it this time too. My heartfelt
OL,13,Fthanks go out to all those hard at
OL,14,Fwork this week."
OL,16,FDr Jack Fletcher, chairman of the
OL,17,FBritish Medical Association's resident
OL,18,Fdoctors committee, said resident
OL,19,Fdoctors "are as keen as (Wes
OL,20,FStreeting) is to bring an end to the
OL,21,Fstrikes".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@PO]{D@IOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,F"The Health Secretary may well be
OL,7,F'disappointed' but he is failing to
OL,8,Facknowledge a deal was taking shape
OL,9,Funtil his Government quietly watered
OL,10,Fit down, reducing the money on the
OL,11,Ftable, then stretching what was left
OL,12,Fover too many years to make it
OL,13,Fworthwhile," Dr Fletcher said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,F"Resident doctors are as keen as he is
OL,7,Fto bring an end to the strikes, but
OL,8,Fhis Government needs to put an offer
OL,9,Fon the table that we can accept and
OL,10,Fwhich doesn't change at the last
OL,11,Fminute. He also needs to stop using
OL,12,Four next generation of consultants as
OL,13,Fa bargaining chip ` taking away 1,000
OL,14,Fposts when patients and the NHS needs
OL,15,Fsenior doctors for the future.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775481061
OL,3,CNHS urges patients to come forward as
OL,4,Cnormal amid 'difficult' six-day strike
OL,6,F"We know that strikes bring disruption
OL,7,F` despite NHS England's assurances
OL,8,Fthat it can maintain the vast majority
OL,9,Fof services running for patients
OL,10,Fduring times of industrial action.
OL,11,FMany senior doctors will be covering
OL,12,Ffor us and whilst that of course
OL,13,Fbenefits patients, we know they are
OL,14,Falso exhausted and as demoralised as
OL,15,Fwe are.
OL,17,F"We are willing to bring an end to
OL,18,Findustrial action, but we are not
OL,19,Fseeing that willingness from
OL,20,FGovernment so far."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
